<div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h2 class="panel-title" style="font-size: 34px;" id="mary-title">Mary</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body story-inactive" id="mary-story">
      <p>It&rsquo;s true that you should take some time off.<br />
        You shouldn&rsquo;t be in love so soon.</p>
      <p>I&rsquo;m gonna remove the word &ldquo;should&rdquo; from your vocabulary.</p>
      <p>It&rsquo;s true you shouldn&rsquo;t have to need me.<br />
