      <p>Forget the others; how could they have known that you belong to me?</p>
      <p>I&rsquo;m gonna hold on for dear life.</p>
      <p>Hold onto you.</p>
      <p>You try so hard not to look at me,<br />
        but it&rsquo;s all in vain,</p>
      <p>for even strangers see the love that&rsquo;s in your eyes.</p>
      <p>Oh, you can&rsquo;t run from me.<br />
        I got my hooks in you.</p>
      <p>And, I&rsquo;m gonna hold on for dear life.</p>
      <p>Hold onto you.</p>
      <p>It&rsquo;s true you never even asked me:<br />
        why should I fall so hard for you?</p>
      <p>And without warning,</p>
      <p>you run and hide yourself a million miles from me.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
    (function() {
        var title2 = document.getElementById('mary-title'),
            content2 = document.getElementById('mary-story');

        title2.addEventListener('mouseover', function() {
            content2.classList.add('story-preview');
        });
        content2.addEventListener('mouseover', function() {
            content2.classList.add('story-preview');
        });
        title2.addEventListener('mouseout', function() {
            content2.classList.remove('story-preview');
        })
        content2.addEventListener('mouseout', function() {
            content2.classList.remove('story-preview');
        })
    })();
</script>